title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 28 2022

description:
Out-of-touch Biden tells Americans to buy generic cereal. Fetterman's pool. With double-digit lead in Florida, DeSantis to campaign for Zeldin in New York. Buck can't wait for a change of guard in his longtime home state after the outrageousness of the crime and covid eras. GOP nominee for Michigan governor Tudor Dixon joins Clay and Buck on the cusp of possibly taking out Gretchen Whitmer. Nancy Pelosi's husband Paul attacked during home invasion.
